{
  "chapter": 6,
  "chapter_summary": "段飞熊来到宝珠山庄，当面追问段玉是否守住碧玉刀和父命。华华凤揭开自己就是朱珠的身份，并说明抛入水中的刀是假刀，真正的碧玉刀仍在朱珠手中。朱二爷认可段玉虽惹麻烦却凭诚实揭破青龙会阴谋，点明他胜过青龙会靠的不是宝刀而是诚实。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_kuan",
      "speaker_name": "朱二爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是不是叫你一定要将那柄碧玉刀送到朱二叔手上的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_fei_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "段老爷子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在你的刀呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我……我太不小心，是我的错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是别人的错？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "华华凤！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么要把碧玉刀抛到水里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "朱珠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我抛下的那柄刀是假的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "朱珠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么要让我着急呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "朱珠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我在吃醋。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "朱珠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "吃谁的醋？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "朱珠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "吃我自己的醋。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_fei_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "段飞熊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只有一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_fei_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "段飞熊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你赶快说出来吧，我实在很想听听。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_fei_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "段老爷子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就因为如此，所以我才不开心。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_fei_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "段老爷子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_fei_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "段老爷子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我错了，我错了，你还说我错了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    }
